title: Colgate Game
content:
Does anybody know the Colgate Game with the tooth man Harald, who had to kill bacterias with a tooth paste "gun"?

If yes, is there a possibility to play it on XP without crashes while filling up the tooth paste tube?
___
- We want "The Universe is Toast" ! - [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-yorp.gif[/img]
